ter）于上演了她的制片人杰克·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">安东诺夫（Jack Antonoff）</a>和他的妻子，<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-substance"><em>毒品</em></a>演员玛格丽特·富利（Margaret Falley）的逮捕，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>周六夜现场</em></a>喜剧演员MarcelloHernánández作为他的<em>SNL</em>角色Domingo。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">佐治亚州亚特兰大的萨布丽娜木匠秀的米莉·鲍比·布朗（Millie Bobby Brown）。 <a href="https://t.co/A4JuCou8G6">pic.twitter.com/a4jucou8g6</a></p><p> - 米莉（Millie）（@Dayofmillie） <a href="https://twitter.com/dayofmillie/status/1849021975852671163?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年10月23日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>据报道，布朗正在参加卡彭特的亚特兰大表演，因为她当时正在这座城市拍摄<em>《陌生人事物</em>》第五个也是最后一个赛季。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/stranger-things-season-five-has-finished-filming-thats-a-wrap-see-you-in-2025-3824124">该节目包裹在12月下旬的最后一次郊游中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">Carpenter将于下个月踏上英国和欧洲的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">“ Short N&#39;Sweet”之旅</a>，然后今年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535#:~:text=Sabrina%20Carpenter%20has%20been%20announced,for%20BST%20Hyde%20Park%202025.&amp;text=The%20'Espresso'%20singer%20will%20perform,Zach%20Bryan%20and%20Hugh%20Jackman.">在伦敦的BST Hyde Park头条新闻</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUkszki1LzXxF0U0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到剩余的门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p>她还将在6月与<a href="https://www.nme.c